c: 2
v: 144
t: "Zvirokwazvo, tinomboona kutendeuka kwechiso chako (Muhammad (SAW)) wakatarisa kudenga. Zvirokwazvo, tichakutendeudza kuQiblah (kwaunotarisa uchinamata) divi richakufadza, nokudaro tendeutsa chiso chako kudivi re Al-Masjid Al-Haraam (nzvimbo tsvene iri kuMakkah). Uye pose pamuri imi vanhu tendeutsai zviso zvenyu (pakunamata) motarisa ikoko. Zvirokwazvo, vanhu vakapiwa Gwaro (maJudha nemaKristu) vanoziva kuti (kutendeuka muchitarisa kuKa’bah kuMakkah pakunamata) ichokwadi kubva kuna Tenzi vavo. Uye Allah havarivari zvose zvavanoita"